How many times have I asked you
to put your crap in the trunk?

04:28.260 --> 04:29.810
Sorry.

04:31.770 --> 04:33.650
Well, looks like you won.

04:33.650 --> 04:37.150
‐ Yeah, looks like.
‐ What?

04:38.280 --> 04:40.830
That was the city championship.

04:42.160 --> 04:43.500
Do I need to drive you

04:43.500 --> 04:45.290
to a victory party or something?

04:46.380 --> 04:48.300
Where were you?

04:48.300 --> 04:49.760
Is that a yes or a no?

04:49.760 --> 04:52.100
We talked about it
this morning. You said...

04:52.100 --> 04:55.150
I said I would try.
What do you want?

04:59.740 --> 05:02.250
Congratulations.
I'm proud of you.

05:04.080 --> 05:06.040
<i>Time's</i> Man of the Year?

05:07.130 --> 05:09.970
<i>Wired's</i> Visionary?

05:09.970 --> 05:11.970
‐ Give me a break.
‐ Stop.

05:11.970 --> 05:13.270
You don't know shit about shit.

05:17.110 --> 05:18.070
Say it again.

05:22.910 --> 05:24.210
You don't know shit about...!

05:25.880 --> 05:29.300
You don't know shit about...!

05:29.300 --> 05:31.930
<i>Dad?</i>

05:31.930 --> 05:36.400
<i>Dad? I hope you get this in time.</i>

05:36.400 --> 05:38.070
<i>I know it's a long shot,</i>

